column2: Very sunny- calm- mod./heavy boat traffic
Mostly sunny- slight breeze- lots of skiers- boats
Lots of suspended algae- more floating vegetation than usual
Rained every day- when sun was out it was too windy to get a reading but today is sunny and calm.
Hot all week. Algae bloom just started. Sunny. Ripples
Sunny-breezy.  Lake has turned over.  Surface temp 58 F.
Ice out 4/22/94. Lac du Flambeau tribe speared 200 walleye 4/24/94.  Sunny-calm today.
Hazy-calm.  2'88" rain since last reading-cloudy all last week.
Storms + 4" rain since last reading- hazy-calm.
Sunny-calm-2" rain since last reading-surface temp. 56 degrees.
Cloudy day.  Lake level: very high
Sunny-breezy.  Lots of rain and wind.
Sunny-calm-surface temp. 57 degrees. lake is turning over.
Partly cloudy. calm. lots of pine pollen on the water.
Rained between 10-12 a.m.. had to wait until 1: 00. sunny and windy.
Have had a lot of rain- today sunny and calm.
First nice day since July 20.  Sunny and calm.
Partly sunny- calm- and ice out on 4/23/01.
Sunny- breezy- and water temperature is down to 60 degrees.
Sunny- calm- and turnover has started.
Sunny (hot).  No rain for a week.
Sunny- hot.  No rain for 2 weeks.
Cloudy- last rain a week ago.
Sunny- no rain for weeks. A lot of eagles on the lake.
cloudy- no rain- loons with little one
cloudy- a lot of green particles in water
Hazy- High clouds. Sun was intermittent.
Cloudy Overcast 64 F Barbara Marshall asst.
Sun and clouds. Light breeze. Waves on water. 70 F Sun with clouds. Light breeze. Small waves on surface. 70F
Party cloudy. Waves on surface from breeze and boat traffic. 77F.
Cloudy overcast 64 F. Barbara Marshall asst.
Partly cloudy 82 F. Some boat traffic. 5mph wind
Sunny No clouds.  68F  wind 5-7 Mph.  Waves and location drifting
Thin cloud cover. 7mph wind. Small waves. 69F
Calm sunny morning. Considerable pine pollen on surface. Visited eagles nest on small island 2 babies. 70 degrees clear for satellite  pass
Sunny. 86F. Slight wind. Some boat traffic
Mostly sunny. Mild boat traffic and waves. Temp 75 F
Mostly sunny. Wispy clouds. Small wave action. 68 F. 6mph wind
Cloudy no sun. Temp. 63F. Light waves. 8 mph wind
Sunny. 3 mph wind. No boat traffic.
Overcast. Calm. No boat traffic. 73 F Overcast. Calm. No boat traffic. 73 F Rain 4 hrs earlier less than 1/4 inch
Clear Sunny sky. Windy from West. Some surface waves. Moderate boat traffic. 62F
